
# Validation + Workflow Engine API  
A FastAPI-based backend system that validates event submissions, calculates delay, applies business rules, and produces workflow decisions (PASS / REVIEW / BLOCK) with scoring.

---

##  Project Overview

This project implements a structured **Validation + Workflow Engine** with:

- Strict input validation
- Clear business rule separation
- Scoring logic
- Decision engine (PASS / REVIEW / BLOCK)
- Database persistence
- Alembic migrations
- Clean architecture

---

## 🏗️ Tech Stack

- FastAPI
- PostgreSQL (Neon DB)
- SQLAlchemy
- Alembic
- Pydantic
- Python 3.10+

---

##  Project Structure

```
## Project Structure

```
REPORTING-SYSTEMS/
│
├── alembic/                     # Database migration scripts
│
├── config/                      # Configuration files (environment / settings if used)
│
├── models/                      # SQLAlchemy database models
│   ├── base.py                  # Base class for all database models
│   └── evaluation_record.py     # EvaluationRecord database model
│
├── router/                      # API route definitions
│   └── evaluation_api.py        # FastAPI endpoints for evaluation workflow
│
├── schemas/                     # Pydantic request/response schemas
│   └── evaluation_record.py     # Request and response data models
│
├── service/                     # Business logic layer
│   ├── validation_service.py    # Input validation rules
│   ├── scoring_service.py       # Scoring calculation logic
│   └── evaluation_service.py    # Workflow decision engine
│
├── venv/                        # Python virtual environment
│
├── .env                         # Environment variables (database URL etc.)
├── .gitignore                   # Git ignored files
├── alembic.ini                  # Alembic configuration
├── main.py                      # FastAPI application entry point
├── requirements.txt             # Project dependencies
└── README.md                    # Project documentation
```
```

